commitResults.messageTitle: Fix styling for sort command usage message

commitResults.messageBody:
Sort command constructor takes in the keyword string.

Parser is in charge of creating the Comparator to sort each contact.
However, we are unable to get the keyword from Comparator. Error
messages and logs are in SortCommand. Hence passing the string to
sort command makes the most sense.

Added another way users are able to sort contacts by. Added a new method
convertDate() to change the String date to a Date object to use java
inbuilt date comparison.

Abstract out maximum date in appointment class. Created a new file for
utility methods related to date.

Added another way users are able to sort contacts by. Added a new method
getPriority that gets the highest priority among all the tags.

Contacts with no tags were ranked higher than contacts with HIGH
priority.

Change value of priority for contacts with no tags.
